---
title: Chorizo Rigatoni with Cherry Tomatoes and Mozzarella
description: The key to this dish is gently roasting the cherry tomatoes and peppers to bring out their natural sweetness and then balancing this against salty olives and mild, creamy mozzarella cheese. We’ve made it super quick and easy, to leave more time for putting your feet up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-rigatoni-90826548.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chorizo-rigatoni-03e1e503.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/chorizo-rigatoni-59022cdb2310a86b8f48c052
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
course: main course
